==Lettuce begin==
===Talking to Kupus Varza===
* '''Kupus Varza:''' Hello young sprout. How can I help you?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|What can you tell me about EOC?}}
** '''Player:''' What can you tell me about EOC?
** '''Kupus Varza:''' Ah, the Evolution of Cabbage. The great cruciferous march of life!
** '''Kupus Varza:''' The cabbages are taking their rightful place in the world, and you can help them.
** '''Kupus Varza:''' Join with me, train your cabbage picking skills, and become part of the evolutionary force!
** '''Player:''' If this is a skill, why isn't it in the skill interface?
** '''Kupus Varza:''' Seriously? Have you seen how little space there is left on that interface?
** '''Kupus Varza:''' Was there anything else you wanted help with?
** {{tact|initial}}
* {{topt|Where can I get a cape like yours?}}
** '''Player:''' Where can I get a cape like yours?
** '''Kupus Varza:''' This? This is a cape of skill mastery, worn by those who have achieved true cabbage picking enlightenment.
** '''Kupus Varza:''' Give yourself over to a life of cabbage picking, and maybe you too will one day be able to wear such a cape.
** '''Kupus Varza:''' Was there anything else you wanted help with?
** {{tact|initial}}
* {{topt|Goodbye.}}
** '''Player:''' Goodbye.
** '''Kupus Varza:''' Go now young sprout, and embrace your destiny!
** {{tact|end}}

